Class Receiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uweo.java2.assignment9.Receiver
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Server.Receiver

    public class Receiver
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates a Receiver object, which performs an action based on its given instance of an AbstractCommand subclass

    slajaunie

        public void action(DivCommand command)
        Executes a given DivCommand, dividing the given command's operand1 into operand2 and setting the given command's result field to the result of that computation. If a given command's operand1 or operand2 fields are set to the BigDecimal value of 0, it logs that an ArithmeticException was thrown and sets the given command's result value to the BogDecimal value of 0.
        Parameters:
        command - an instance of DivCommand
